<h3 id="把一个文件合并成一行">把一个文件合并成一行</h3>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="nb">awk </span>BEGIN<span class="o">{</span><span class="nv">RS</span><span class="o">=</span>EOF<span class="o">}</span><span class="s1">'{gsub(/\n/,",");print}'</span> aa.txt
<span class="c">#awk默认将记录分隔符（record separator即RS）设置为\n</span>
<span class="c">#此行代码将RS设置为EOF（文件结束），也就是把文件视为一个记录</span>
<span class="c">#然后通过gsub函数将\n替换成","，最后输出</span></code></pre></figure>

<h3 id="两个文件相同key-累加并倒序输出">两个文件，相同key 累加，并倒序输出</h3>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="nb">cat </span>a1 a2 | <span class="nb">awk</span>  <span class="s1">'{a[$2]+=$1;}END{for(i in a){print a[i]" "i;}}'</span> |sort <span class="nt">-k1</span> <span class="nt">-nr</span>
<span class="c"># END</span></code></pre></figure>

